    <item>
      <title>setting timed events in puppet</title>
      <link>https://purpleidea.com/blog/2012/11/14/setting-timed-events-in-puppet/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Nov 2012 01:31:43 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://purpleidea.com/blog/2012/11/14/setting-timed-events-in-puppet/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve tried to push puppet to its limits, and so far I&amp;rsquo;ve succeeded. When you hit &lt;a href=&#34;http://projects.puppetlabs.com/issues/1565&#34;&gt;the kind of bug that forces you to hack around it&lt;/a&gt;, you know you are close. In any case, this isn&amp;rsquo;t about that embarrassing bug, it&amp;rsquo;s about how to set delayed actions in puppet.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Enter puppet-runonce, a module that I&amp;rsquo;ve just finished writing. It starts off with the realization that you can exec an action which also writes to a file. If it sees this file, then it knows that it has already completed, and shouldn&amp;rsquo;t run itself again. The relevant parts are here:&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-ruby&#34; data-lang=&#34;ruby&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;define runonce&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a2f&#34;&gt;exec&lt;/span&gt;(&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b8860b&#34;&gt;$command&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b44&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;/bin/true&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;,&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b8860b&#34;&gt;$notify&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a2f;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;undef&lt;/span&gt;,&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b8860b&#34;&gt;$repeat_on_failure&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a2f&#34;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;) {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a2f&#34;&gt;include&lt;/span&gt; runonce&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a2f&#34;&gt;exec&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;base&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b8860b&#34;&gt;$date&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b44&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;/bin/date &amp;gt;&amp;gt; /var/lib/puppet/tmp/runonce/exec/${name}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b8860b&#34;&gt;$valid_command&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b8860b&#34;&gt;$repeat_on_failure&lt;/span&gt; ? {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a2f&#34;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b44&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;${date} &amp;amp;&amp;amp; ${command}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;,&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        default &lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b44&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;${command} &amp;amp;&amp;amp; ${date}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;,&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a2f&#34;&gt;exec&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b44&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;runonce-exec-${name}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        command &lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b44&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;${valid_command}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;,&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        creates &lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b44&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;/var/lib/puppet/tmp/runonce/exec/${name}&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;,    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#080;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;# run once&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        notify &lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b8860b&#34;&gt;$notify&lt;/span&gt;,&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#080;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;# TODO: add any other parameters here that users wants such as cwd and environment...&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a2f&#34;&gt;require&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#800&#34;&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#b44&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;/var/lib/puppet/tmp/runonce/exec/&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;,&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
